page.content: {Local Businesses (cont) 11.Colin King Printers 12.Waste Paper Reclamation 13.Belcher's Fish and Game 14.Thwaites Toys - cottage industry 15.Secretarial Services 16.Beechcroft Ironworks - mainly gates 17.Elm Leisure - swimming pools, etc 18.M.G.Motors - supplies for M.G. cars 19.Cambridge Joinery - window frames 20.Cambridge Marquees - loan service 21.P.D.Sillence - Signwriter 22.J.P.Soft Furnishing - chair covers 23.J & M Carpet Cleaning Service. Some people sell garden produce out side their gates.A number of builders, decorators, plumbers and window cleaners reside here.Several mobile shops visit: fish van, hardware, and mobile library. A farrier visits every 5 weeks. There are 3 Public Houses in Over.
